title: ddfprod 5185 - Sophie Moone
description:
Sandy's Fantasies (sandysfantasies.com) by ddfprod (Denys Defrancesco) - series 5185s and 5185vsv - Sophie Moone (aka Sophie Sweet).

Sandy's Fantasies used to be one of ddfprod's websites, hosted by the beautiful lesbian(?) model Sandy (or Zsanett Egerhazi as she's known in Budapest, Hungary). The site features also lots of photoshoots with Sophie Moone (aka Sophie Sweet in some sites). Today the site is still there, but it's been a while since they updated it.

I've got at least 100 good photoshoots of Sandy, Sophie Moone and their friends in solo, girl-girl and hc action. Anyone interested? Send a comment, and I'll upload some more.
